/-- Suen finite-transfer main capstone with the rough-range inequality
discharged by a certified empty rough-large range.

This keeps the same Suen and finite-transfer hypotheses as
`main_suen_finite_transfer_range_bounds_concrete_euler_smooth_cutoff_on_range_and_initial`,
but replaces the raw rough-range inequality by the stronger certificate-shaped
condition `roughLargeCount (zNatScale N) N = 0`. -/
theorem main_suen_finite_transfer_rough_zero_concrete_euler_smooth_cutoff_on_range_and_initial
    {ι : Type*}
    (cls : ℕ → Finset ι)
