    exact (R m).red_class_mem_large N hN (le_trans (hTred_le m hm) hTN) s hs r hr
  · intro N m hN hTN hm _hm_log s hs b hb
    exact (R m).red_class_bound_large N hN (le_trans (hTred_le m hm) hTN) s hs b hb
  · intro N m hN hTN hm _hm_log
    exact fixedNumeratorPaperReducedClassEnvelopeInputs_red_class_uniform_sum_large
      (R m) N hN (le_trans (hTred_le m hm) hTN)

/-- Direct reduced-sum bound from the paper's raw uniform reduced-class
