/-- Direct-output separated analytic/reduced-envelope fixed-`m` endpoint.

Unlike the older packaged alias route, this theorem uses the separate reduced
record `R` to prove the direct reduced-sum estimate.  The only compatibility
conditions are that the reduced carrier and reduced cutoff named by `R` agree
with the analytic record's public carrier and cutoff. -/
theorem fixed_m_paper_suen_analytic_and_reduced_envelope_direct_reduced_sum_full_outputs_and_final_standard_tail
    {ι κ : Type*} [DecidableEq κ] {m : ℕ}
